\begin{alertblock}{System Components}

The Telescope consists of several discrete, but interacting blocks
\begin{itemize}
  \item \textbf{In Beam}
  \begin{itemize}
    \item 8x Silicon micro-strip Sensors
    \item 32x \textbf{Analog-Pipeline Chip\--128} for pulse-height sampling/readout
    \item Mount/Signal Routing Printed Circuit Boards
  \end{itemize}
  \item \textbf{Out of Beam}
  \begin{itemize}
    \item An FPGA-Based Data Acquisition (DAQ) Board
    \item A USB-3 Connected PC with DAQ/analysis software
  \end{itemize}
\end{itemize}

\end{alertblock}

